GETTING HERE
/$
$
From the turnpike
:
Head south to exit 49 - Hollywood Blvd/Pines Blvd, Hollywood
​
Make sure you take the exit that is AFTER the bridge, not before or you will have to make a u-turn.
​
Once you get off of the turnpike, head east. The first light is 62nd Avenue. If you pass 441/St. Road 7, you went too far.
Go south on 62 Avenue until you pass Miramar Parkway. Once you pass Miramar Parkway, keep an eye out for 35 court. Head east on 35 court.
​
LaPalm Trailer Park will be on the south side of the road.
​
From I-95:
Head south on I-95 to exit 18 - FL-858, Hallandale Beach Blvd
​
Head west on Hallandale Blvd. The first light after 441/St. Rd 7 will be 62nd Avenue. Head south on 62nd Avenue
to 35th Court.
​
Head east on 35 Court. LaPalm Trailer Park will be on the south side of the road.
